{"tid":1067381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有另一半記得好好珍惜","createTime":"2019-03-18T13:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T16:14:33.000Z","uid":132434,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fec75add20a79e8cd2dbf52875d47931ce0f73a6","tid":1067381,"uid":132434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"投入好多 付出好多<br />\n或者有時都有脾氣唔好 發晦氣既時候<br />\n但真係努力溝通咗 先再小心下決定<br />\n千其唔好衝動講分手<br />\n要好好珍惜 <br />\n唔好因爲一時貪玩而破壞信任<br />\n一旦有裂縫 就好難修補<br />\n總之拍拖真係唔可以自私<br />\n<br />\n利申 拍過幾次 到最後都發現對方背住自己 <br />\n做啲破壞關係同信任既事 <br />\n甚至根本唔係鍾意我 <br />\n去愛人真係一件好攰既事<br />\n感覺自己既感情已經磨蝕哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea02582b979a6a7bda3f0280885516b3d3151607","tid":1067381,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"啱  我都係一世單身好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9822d0cd6d54a14096517c08b95665c5bf508ee2","tid":1067381,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"今日分咗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680ac89c2105aa640ee0b843fe04fc8091a2ba21","tid":1067381,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"17531a3913e362a753908851684822c8b10b2073","tid":1067381,"uid":44435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}